{
  "stem": "10768.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Two very nice girls, my age, were hidden by Gentiles, apparently because they liked them or perhaps they were hoping that after the war, their-- the money that they will dig out from somewhere.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know what ulterior motive they had.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the fact is the others who survived from our town are only the ones who were sent from our town by Stalin deep to Russia and came back in 1947 or whenever the influx was from the Russian territory back.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "From, from that town Zaslaw, yeah-- no, not Zaslaw, excuse me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Zaslaw, I'm mixing up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Zlotow on the German territory where our hospital was first, where that huge offensive was and so many-- so many injured.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were told again, go deeper in the road towards Berlin.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "At that time, on one of the roads, we were totally surrounded-- not exactly by the German Army, but by leftover units who couldn't run away fast enough.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were running so far, or maybe they couldn't run so fast.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were going on the tracks, that we were surrounded.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were staying in woods.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We didn't have enough food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We had the three trucks only.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the Germans were around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we were told we cannot go forwards, and nobody from the back can come to us because the roads are unsafe.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we were there probably a week or more, surrounded by the Germans until they sort of like thinned out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Some of them maybe went to their own homes or they undressed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But until the road got safe and, and we continued until we came-- already in April, we came to a town which was called Biesenthal.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And in my opinion, it was south of Berlin, perhaps 35, 40 kilometers south of Berlin.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
